Doubly-linked list/Element insertion

{{task|Data Structures}}Use the link structure defined in <a class="rosetta__link--rosetta" href="http://rosettacode.org/wiki/Doubly-Linked List (element)]] to define a procedure for inserting a link into a doubly-linked list. Call this procedure to insert element C into a list {A,B}, between elements A and B.

This is much like inserting into a [[Singly-Linked List (element insertion)" title="Doubly-Linked List (element)]] to define a procedure for inserting a link into a doubly-linked list. Call this procedure to insert element C into a list {A,B}, between elements A and B.

This is much like inserting into a [[Singly-Linked List (element insertion)">Singly-Linked List</a>, but with added assignments so that the backwards-pointing links remain correct.

